\theta(x,t)
\nabla\phi(x,t)+{d^2\over dt^2}\vec v(t)
\nabla \theta(x,t)
\nabla \phi(x,t)=(\frac{\partial\phi (x,t)}{\partial x_1},...,\frac{\partial\phi (x,t)}{\partial x_n})
v(t)=(v_1(t),...,v_n(t))
\theta
\theta (x,t)=\phi(x,t)+x_1\frac{d^2 v_1(t)}{dt^2}+...+x_n\frac{d^2 v_n(t)}{dt^2}
\nabla \theta(x,t)=\nabla\phi(x,t)+\frac{d^2 v(t)}{dt^2}
